    {
      "name": "How To Set Up CUB",
      "type": "text",
      "title": {
        "show": true,
        "level": 1
      },
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>You can make the condition show on a token when the player mark it on the Actor Sheet with the module Combat Utility Belt.</p><p>First you need to enable Condition Lab.</p><img src=\"modules/masks-newgeneration-unofficial/images/guide/cub-masks02.webp\" width=\"749\" height=\"454\" /><p> </p><p>You need to create a trigger On and Off to each condition.</p><img src=\"modules/masks-newgeneration-unofficial/images/guide/cub-masks01.webp\" width=\"800\" height=\"711\" /><p> </p><p>This is the values you can use for each condition:</p><p>Afraid</p><p>data.attrLeft.conditions.options.0.value</p><p>Angry </p><p>data.attrLeft.conditions.options.1.value</p><p>Guilty </p><p>data.attrLeft.conditions.options.2.value</p><p>Hopeless </p><p>data.attrLeft.conditions.options.3.value</p><p>Insecure</p><p>data.attrLeft.conditions.options.4.value</p><p> </p><p>You need to create the conditions. You can import then using this link: <a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/brunocalado/masks-newgeneration-unofficial/main/resources/cub-pbta-condition-map.json\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Download Link</a></p><img src=\"modules/masks-newgeneration-unofficial/images/guide/cub-masks03.webp\" width=\"800\" height=\"477\" /><p>Make sure each condition has its triggers defined.</p><p> </p><h2>Icons</h2><p>Angry: icons/skills/wounds/injury-face-impact-orange.webp</p><img src=\"icons/skills/wounds/injury-face-impact-orange.webp\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" /><p> </p><p>Afraid: icons/magic/unholy/silhouette-robe-evil-power.webp</p><img src=\"icons/magic/unholy/silhouette-robe-evil-power.webp\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" /><p> </p><p>Guilty: icons/creatures/mammals/humanoid-cat-skulking-teal.webp</p><img src=\"icons/creatures/mammals/humanoid-cat-skulking-teal.webp\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" /><p> </p><p>Hopeless: icons/creatures/magical/spirit-undead-masked-blue.webp</p><img src=\"icons/creatures/magical/spirit-undead-masked-blue.webp\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" /><p> </p><p>Insecure: icons/skills/wounds/injury-face-impact-orange.webp</p><img src=\"icons/magic/death/undead-skeleton-deformed-red.webp\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" /><p> </p><p> </p>"
      },
