    {
      "name": "Macros",
      "type": "text",
      "title": {
        "show": true,
        "level": 1
      },
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>You have a macro to let your players change labels easier.</p><p> </p><p> </p><img src=\"icons/commodities/treasure/mask-jeweled-gold.webp\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /><p>Label Changer</p><ol><li>Import the macro to the world. </li><li>Share it with your players.</li><li>They must select their token. </li></ol><p> </p><img src=\"modules/masks-newgeneration-unofficial/images/guide/macro-labelchanger.png\" width=\"397\" height=\"334\" /><p> </p><p>Notes</p><p>The token must be linked to the actor.</p>"
      },
